verbose_text: Jasplakinolide significantly decreased the pause frequency of S135A vesicles (89.2% +/- 1.4%, p = 0.001) and WT vesicles (90.3% +/- 1.4%, p = 0.001) but had no effect on S135E vesicles, whereas the pause duration of S135A and S135E vesicles was increased by jasplakinolide to the same level (121.4% +/- 7.1%, 122.5% +/- 6.0%, and 119.4% +/- 5.5% for WT, S135A, and S135E vesicles, respectively).
evidence: duration of S135A and S135E vesicles was increased by jasplakinolide
